  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "庚子西狩丛谈卷之四上",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_10_37358-37801",
          "range": "37358-37801",
          "rangeStart": 37358,
          "rangeEnd": 37801,
          "markText": "荣相亦正备启程，乘舆已驾，门内外均鹄立伺候。匆促出见，词意甚殷渥，谓：“君既定南向履新，咱们异日须在都中把晤矣。”予谓：“岭海万里，从此瞻天路远，正恐趋侍无期。”曰：“这何至此？”予曰：“道缺循例须六年俸满，始可送部引见。法令所定，安能自由？”曰：“尔尽放心前去，要回京都，这还不容易么？早则年底，迟则明春，准可在都相见。暂时小别，勿惓惓也。”予伺送之升舆，立即飞驰出城，至黄河岸口，勘视辇道船渡。适瞿大军机随后至，于黄幄外相值。瞿曰：“渔川何来？”予谓：“来此照看河渡。”瞿又问：“曾见荣相否？”予曰：“适从荣相寓中来。”曰：“荣相何言？”予曰：“匆匆并无他语。”瞿曰：“总有数语。”予即以所言者具述之。瞿即含笑点首曰：“好，好。既是荣相说过，旦晚许可陛见，那是准靠得住的。大喜，大喜，今年内定可回京相见也。”盖予彼时全不识官场机械，直心爽口，一无隐讳。不意瞿固疑予厚荣相而薄于彼，以此探予，予顷所言，适触其忌。后来，瞿之屡相阻厄，其几即始于此。少年粗率，自招其咎，真俗所谓冒失者也。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1774155932,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-03-22 13:05:32",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=37358&rangeEnd=37801",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=37358&rangeEnd=37801"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_10_24210-24310",
          "range": "24210-24310",
          "rangeStart": 24210,
          "rangeEnd": 24310,
          "markText": "公平素最服膺曾文正公，启口必称“我老师”，敬佩殆如神圣。尝告予：“文正公，你太丈人，是我老师，你可惜未曾见着，予生也晚呵！我老师文正公，那真是大人先生。现在这些大人先生，简直都是秕糠，我一扫而空之。”",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758078601,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-17 11:10:01",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=24210&rangeEnd=24310",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=24210&rangeEnd=24310"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_10_23512-23771",
          "range": "23512-23771",
          "rangeStart": 23512,
          "rangeEnd": 23771,
          "markText": "我办了一辈子的事，练兵也，海军也，都是纸糊的老虎，何尝能实在放手办理？不过勉强涂饰，虚有其表，不揭破犹可敷衍一时。如一间破屋，由裱糊匠东补西贴，居然成一净室，虽明知为纸片糊裱，然究竟决不定里面是何等材料，即有小小风雨，打成几个窟孔[插图]，随时补葺，亦可支吾对付。乃必欲爽手扯破，又未预备何种修葺材料，何种改造方式，自然真相破露，不可收拾。但裱糊匠又何术能负其责？",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758078399,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-17 11:06:39",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=23512&rangeEnd=23771",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=23512&rangeEnd=23771"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_10_26204-26266",
          "range": "26204-26266",
          "rangeStart": 26204,
          "rangeEnd": 26266,
          "markText": "予当时听之，意用何在，亦殊不甚明白。仔细推敲，大抵谓天下事在局外呐喊议论，总是无益，必须躬自入局，挺膺负责，乃有成事之可冀。",
          "colorStyle": 2,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758072097,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-17 09:21:37",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=26204&rangeEnd=26266",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=26204&rangeEnd=26266"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "庚子西狩丛谈卷之三",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_9_22852-22947",
          "range": "22852-22947",
          "rangeStart": 22852,
          "rangeEnd": 22947,
          "markText": "先是两宫襆被出都，过昌平州，知州裴敏中方抱重病，霸昌道凤昌因先期未奉有廷旨，车驾至城下，疑为假托赚门，坚闭不纳，且从城上鸣枪示威。两宫不得已，乃绕城奔驰，盖恐洋兵之蹑其后也。太后因此甚愤愤。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758595974,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-23 10:52:54",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=22852&rangeEnd=22947",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=22852&rangeEnd=22947"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_9_22275-22308",
          "range": "22275-22308",
          "rangeStart": 22275,
          "rangeEnd": 22308,
          "markText": "宫监对于皇上，殊不甚为意，虽称之为万岁爷，实际不啻为彼辈播弄傀儡。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758595171,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-23 10:39:31",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=22275&rangeEnd=22308",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=22275&rangeEnd=22308"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_9_21726-21747",
          "range": "21726-21747",
          "rangeStart": 21726,
          "rangeEnd": 21747,
          "markText": "大臣不言小臣言之，却未顾及越分逾等之嫌也。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758595075,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-23 10:37:55",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21726&rangeEnd=21747",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=21726&rangeEnd=21747"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_9_20849-20964",
          "range": "20849-20964",
          "rangeStart": 20849,
          "rangeEnd": 20964,
          "markText": "俞则更丝毫不问，每日但向予诋毁岑氏，凡岑之一言一动，皆向予报告，极口肆詈。予当时阅世过浅，不免时有随声附和之处。讵彼于岑前诋予，亦复如是，并将予语一一转报，而益加之以添砌，反复唆弄。致予与岑恶感日深，至结不解之仇者，俞尤与有力也。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758594850,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-23 10:34:10",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20849&rangeEnd=20964",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=20849&rangeEnd=20964"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_9_14906-14961",
          "range": "14906-14961",
          "rangeStart": 14906,
          "rangeEnd": 14961,
          "markText": "方在沙城将启銮时，天甫向明，在行宫门前，岑一见予即相诟怨曰：“谢尔厚意，乃以此破沙锅向我头上套，令我无辜受累。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758591716,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-23 09:41:56",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=14906&rangeEnd=14961",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=14906&rangeEnd=14961"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300157270_9_11752-11787",
          "range": "11752-11787",
          "rangeStart": 11752,
          "rangeEnd": 11787,
          "markText": "盖诸公俱疑予意图规避，而特藉地方为饰词，似天下决无真为百姓计较之官者。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1758591003,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2025-09-23 09:30:03",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300157270&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11752&rangeEnd=11787",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/44f32e20813aba3efg0109be?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=11752&rangeEnd=11787"
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "reviewId": "32618646_83n4HTi9O",
          "range": "24806-24809",
          "chapterName": "庚子西狩丛谈卷之三",
          "content": "cén chūn xuān\n（1861—1933）广西西林人，原名春泽，字云阶。岑毓英子。清光绪举人。1898年（光绪二十四年）任广东布政使，旋调任甘肃布政使。八国联军攻陷北京时，率兵护送慈禧太后和光绪帝至西安，升陕西巡抚。历任四川、两广、云贵总督，多次镇压反清斗争。1907年调任邮传部尚书。因与袁世凯争权，解职。1911年（宣统三年）四川保路运动兴起后，起用为四川总督，见清廷大势已去，未赴任。长期在西南活动。1916年护国运动期间，与梁启超在广东肇庆成立军务院，任副抚军长，代行抚军长职权。1917年参加护法运动，次年联络桂系军阀改组军政府，排挤孙中山，自任护法军政府主席总裁。1920年被粤军驱逐，寓居上海、苏州。著有《乐斋漫笔》。",
